<h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">4 Case-Changing Tactics Legal Videographers Use</h1>
<div class="main_content_body">
	<p style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;">Feb 10 2015 | posted by Giles-Parscale</p>
